room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Escape in 60 in Cleveland
review: Me and my friends had an excellent time in the Bank Heist. Definitely coming back for the other 3 rooms!

room_title: Escape room "Bank Heist" by Escape in 60 in Cleveland
review: We did the Bank Heist yesterday, we were so close but missed getting the gold out the door. We had an absolute blast! We will be coming back again to try another room. The staff was great. It was a nice day in Cleveland and my relatives from Mississippi had a great time!
